            <h1>Sport Report - Professional Soccer Toddler, Golf Innovations & Washington Redskins Charm Offensive<a class="arrow" href="#"></a></h1>

            <div class="info">
                <ul>
                    <li class="airDate">
                        <span>Aired:&nbsp;</span>
                                                    03/26/14
                                            </li>
                    <li class="viewCount">
                        &nbsp;&#124;&nbsp;<span>Views:&nbsp;</span>214,784
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p class="description">A Belgian soccer team signs a 20-month-old baby, the PGA attempts to make golf more interesting, and the Washington Redskins extend an olive branch to Native Americans.&nbsp;(8:17)</p>
                                    <div class="tags">
